Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是地球軍宇宙戰鬥艦Dominion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archangel 能聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜塔爾...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 敵艦的光學影像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同型艦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久不見了 拉米亞斯艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾我們要以這種形式重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helderton和Heusinger留在這裏不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殖民衛星Mendel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果順利的話能解決很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這感覺 難道是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我「大叔」ZAFT在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sledgehammer 瞄準敵人M.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.33,0:01:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(600,600)\fs33\fscy130\b0}PHASE-42 螺旋的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要機體沒事就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 該死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:03:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閃開 庫洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打壞了會挨罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼呢 快點 繼續攻擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下 會擊中友軍機體的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擊中了也沒關係 有Trans Phase 裝甲的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archangel接近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gottfried瞄準 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是有ZAFT在 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之要去確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是的話就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對面的港口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 請盡快讓Eternal出發
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動不了的話 就只能交給他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確是如此 DaCosta
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike Buster?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這回換你駕駛那個了嗎 穆·拉·布拉加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新機型嗎 這裝備可能會不利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 你這傢伙 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏尼!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 用了這麼長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我們失算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最大推力 追上Dominion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別再被纏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helldart 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valiant 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞沙琪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢用提亞哥的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會在這裏和你戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勞·盧·克魯澤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太高興了 穆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離 20 Orange 15 Mark 1 Alpha
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧布 Izumo級戰艦正接近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 已經自由了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gottfried 1號2號 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時撤退 發射信號彈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在情況對我們不利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已將他們逼到這種地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三架機體的能量也快用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不撤退的話會敗的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你既然這麼說 下次就能贏了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想死在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valiant 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射信號彈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右舷10 脫離戰鬥區域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏尼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命令撤退了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...但那傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在要撤退了 你還想再受苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連把握撤退的時機都如此了得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜塔爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 阿斯蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是那些駕駛員...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在奧布時也感覺到了 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很難相信他們是正規軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是Natural
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  布拉加和艾爾斯曼有消息了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 今天一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提亞哥 提亞哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 無法與殖民衛星內部取得通信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這可惡的Natural
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休想 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提亞哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家趁現在進行補給和維修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice沒有問題 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用 Dominion還沒有完全撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯蘭還是留在這
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我不會亂來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各艦請盡快進行補給和維修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果ZAFT軍真的在對面的港口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事態又會是緊迫的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在還不能在這裏被擊敗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提亞哥 真的是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼會和Strike並肩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你活著我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但 事情如果是這樣的話我是不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提亞哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快離開這 別再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 伊扎克 你也一樣 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 別變得像我和阿斯蘭那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯蘭?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放下槍 談談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還以為你能在這裏將我擊敗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 看來你不是那塊料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:14:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終究 孩子是無法戰勝父親的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然命運是在我這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就做個了結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就跟我來 我會親自為你超度的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒天真到會輕易相信敵人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道這是什麼地方嗎 穆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪過啊 你竟不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉...大和? 他還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裏用CNT膠覆蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再被擊中一次就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就貼上護身符什麼的 祈禱別被擊中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說將艦橋斷路器以B號線進行並排增設
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後與Bank25的二極管排列連接
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二班 加緊測定預備操作器的張緊力度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞沙琪 返回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有三艘Nazca級戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在對面港口 碎石的陰影部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三艘Nazca級嗎 陣容真是龐大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dominion呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依然沒有移動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望布拉加他們能帶回些情報
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 誰的部隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是克魯澤隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以穆會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他能夠感覺到 雖然他自己不清楚為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他能感覺到勞·盧·克魯澤的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真高興連你也來了 基拉 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你就是Freedom的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能就那樣在外面等著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我怎麼向瑪琉艦長報告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穆 你受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你 要用那東西的話就把保險解除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣 過來吧 到這開始之地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 這裏也是你出生的故鄉 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要上當 那傢伙說的話不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你變成了我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得我有變成你的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別胡扯了 你這個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有要背叛PLANTs
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是將Natural...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再繼續默然地遵從軍隊的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只為了將Natural全部消滅的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懷念嗎 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道這裏? 我?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何您都不願接受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時候應該請求援軍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是暫時撤退 重新陣勢後再發動攻擊 然而...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做的話 不就讓ZAFT搶先了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙也很快就能行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.84,0:20:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會殺你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟你們好不容易才來到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你們知道一切之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父親?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但留在這 是無法打開那扇門的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很想知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類無盡慾望的終點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以進步之名 追逐瘋狂的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些愚者的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟 你也是其中的一個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.31,0:23:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勞·盧·克魯澤口中說出的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是歷史的陰影 人類的黑暗
